3. Transition the issue to `done`. Run EXACTLY this one command as the final
   step of your session, before stopping:

   ```
   curl -sf -X PATCH "{{paperclipApiUrl}}/api/issues/{{taskId}}" \
     -H "Authorization: Bearer $PAPERCLIP_AGENT_JWT" \
     -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
     -d '{"status":"done"}'
