   The `PAPERCLIP_AGENT_JWT` env var is a short-lived, per-run bearer
   injected by the adapter. It is scoped to this agent + run only. Do NOT
   call any other endpoint with it. Do NOT echo it to stdout.
4. Stop. Your stdout reply is captured as the issue comment; the PATCH
   above transitions the status.
